 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每次係觀塘線喺旺角轉車過對面時，成日都要撞開啲企中間嘅撚樣</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a178a1e3546ef026dde3a64571c1a2ee338bd884","tid":345213,"uid":8648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T06:14:21.000Z","msg":"聽講將個八達通放係閪到嘟會有折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d18b4320868f35764cb8395d6eec406ae72aaeb","tid":345213,"uid":31749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23865bf391638aed8c8decddc036effdf2ddd306","tid":345213,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:03:30.000Z","msg":"積下口德啦屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1cdf3273e3f18fcdb973f671aed5bfcc9e5cb2","tid":345213,"uid":4420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有個d前面嘟完企撚左係度等前面過左先嘟既on9<br />\n其實你地知唔知係可以前面未過就嘟架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過有次前面條友原來嘟唔撚到張卡<br />\n但我未等佢過就嘟<br />\n結果變相我嘟左俾佢過<br />\n而我就入唔到閘<br />\n攪到要我大叫佢返轉頭嘟返佢張卡俾我入<br />\n果條仆街D口吻同眼神仲要覺得係我一個人錯晒<br />\n果刻真係好撚老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91df533887411fffcb2d7dc3f3aa2a138c11412d","tid":345213,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:15:33.000Z","msg":"不過話時話依家啲入閘機好似真係廢左好多<br />\n好多時拎埋張卡出嚟放上去都可以無反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換過張新既會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df68c025537df9db38bd1972ced06e2fab6a628f","tid":345213,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>磨黎磨去感應唔到好似係部機嘅錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解你呢個comment咁多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma